ial {\textless}i{\textgreater}p{\textless}/i{\textgreater}CO{\textless}sub{\textgreater}2{\textless}/sub{\textgreater}. Total ocean volume with dissolved oxygen concentrations of ‚Äâ‚â§‚Äâ‚ÄØ50‚ÄØ¬µmol‚ÄØkg{\textless}sup{\textgreater}‚àí1{\textless}/sup{\textgreater} increases by 2.4, 5.0, and 10.5‚ÄØ{\%} for the 2‚ÄØ√ó, 4‚ÄØ√ó, and 8‚Äâ√ó‚ÄØCO{\textless}sub{\textgreater}2{\textless}/sub{\textgreater} simulations, respectively.{\textless}/p{\textgreater}},
